#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
#Proceso de saldo de pedidos PRIVALIA
#####################################
#VERSIÓN 2.0
#------------------------------------
#Saldo de los pedidos de Privalia Italia
#######################################

$ACTION
#Infbox ACTION
Case ACTION
  When "OUVRE_BATCH"    : Gosub TRT_INI
  When "EXEC"           : Gosub EXEC_SALDO
  When "TERMINE"        : Gosub TERMINE_SALDO
  When "INIT"           : Gosub INIT_DIA_SALDO
  When "OK"             : Gosub OK_SALDO
  When "END"            : Gosub END_SALDO
Endcase

Return

$TRT_INI
  If !clalev([F:SOH])      : Local File SORDER         [SOH] :  Endif
  If !clalev([F:ZINTE])    : Local File ZINTEGRADOR    [ZINTE]: Endif
  If !clalev([F:SOQ])      : Local File SORDERQ        [SOQ] : Endif
  If !clalev([F:SOP])      : Local File SORDERP        [SOP] : Endif
  If !clalev([F:ZPP])      : Local File ZPEDPRIV       [ZPP] : Endif

  If clalev([M:ORDK])=0 Local Mask ORDK [ORDK] Endif
  If clalev([M:ALP])=0 Local Mask ALLPAR [ALP] Endif
  If clalev([F:SOH])<=0  : Local File SORDER     [SOH2] : Endif
Return

$ERRBATCH
  Call ECR_TRACE(errmes$(errn)-num$(errl)-errm,1) From GESECRAN
End

$EXEC_SALDO
  Gosub TRT_INI

  If GSERVEUR
    Onerrgo ERRBATCH
    Call ECR_TRACE("Inicio saldo de pedidos de venta MKT",0) From GESECRAN
  Else
    Call OUVRE_TRACE("Inicio saldo de pedidos de venta MKT") From LECFIC
  Endif

  WMSG = "Saldo pedidos de venta MKT"
  Call ECR_TRACE(WMSG,0) From GESECRAN
  Call ECR_TRACE(mess(174,100,1),-1) From GESECRAN
  Call ECR_TRACE(mess(51,9010,1),-1) From GESECRAN

  Gosub SALDAR_PEDIDO_NEW
  Gosub SALDAR_PEDIDO_TODORUPTURA
  #Gosub SALDAR_PEDIDO_EXCEL
  #Gosub SALDAR_PEDIDO_2

  End
  Return

$TERMINE_SALDO
Return

$INIT_DIA_SALDO
Return

$OK_SALDO
Return

$END_SALDO
Return

$SALDAR_PEDIDO

  Local Char VALBOUT(250),PARBOUT(250)(1..20)
  Local Char NUMPED(50)
  Local Char REFERENCIA(100)
  Local Char CRITERIO(255)
  Local Integer WZGSERVEUR
  Local Char CURRDATE(50)
  Local Char CURRTIME(50)
  Local Char CURRDATETIME_STR(100)
  Local Char REQUEST(100)
  Local Char PEDABIERTO(40)
  Local Decimal CTDRUPTURA

  CURRDATE = (num$(day(date$))) + "/" + num$(month(date$)) + "/" + num$(year(date$))
  CURRTIME = num$(time$)

  CURRDATETIME_STR =CURRDATE + " " + CURRTIME

  #Infbox(CURRDATETIME_STR)

  #End

  WZGSERVEUR = GSERVEUR
  GSERVEUR = 1


  #Leemos todos los pedidos que no estén saldados y cuyos campos especiales estén rellenos
  CRITERIO=
& "[F:SOH]BPCORD='43001877' AND [F:SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT='' AND [F:SOH]ZFIMPEDMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENCONMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFIMSHIPMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENTRACMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENSHIPMKT<>'' AND"
&  + " [F:SOH]ORDSTA=1"

  Filter [F:SOH] Where evalue(CRITERIO)
  For [F:SOH]
    NUMPED=[F:SOH]SOHNUM
    REFERENCIA=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF

    PARBOUT(1)=NUMPED
    PARBOUT(2)="SSH"
    FLGEXE=1

    WSAVFNC = GFONCTION
    GFONCTION = "FUNCLEAR"

    PEDABIERTO=""
    REQUEST="SELECT LCKSYM_0 FROM APLLCK WHERE LCKSYM_0='SOH"+NUMPED+"'"
    For (Char NUMPED(100)) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [YYY]
      PEDABIERTO = [F:YYY]NUMPED
    Next

    If PEDABIERTO="" Then
      #Comprobamos que el pedido tenga algún artículo en ruptura
      CTDRUPTURA=0
      REQUEST="SELECT SUM(SHTQTY_0) AS CANTIDAD FROM SORDERQ WHERE SOHNUM_0='"+NUMPED+"'"
      For (Decimal CTDRUP) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [ZZZ]
        CTDRUPTURA = [F:ZZZ]CTDRUP
      Next

      If CTDRUPTURA>0 Then
        Call ECR_TRACE("SALDANDO PEDIDO: "+NUMPED,0) From GESECRAN

        Update [SOH] Where SOHNUM=[F:SOH]SOHNUM With ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR
        Update [ZINTE] Where ZREF1=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF With ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR

        GACTION="TRTCLESOH"

        Call TRAITE_CHAR(VALBOUT,PARBOUT,"","TRTVENCDE","",1,"XYTRTVENCDE") From GTRAITE

        GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR
      Endif
    Else
      Call ECR_TRACE("******** PEDIDO "+NUMPED+ " NO SE PUDO SALDAR. ABIERTO EN OTRO PUESTO",0) From GESECRAN
    Endif

    #If fstat
    #  GOK=0 : Call FSTA("TRTCLESOH") From GLOCK : STA=14
    #Endif
    If GOK<0 : Goto ROLL_SAL_PEDIDO
    Elsif !GOK : Goto AB_SAL_PEDIDO
    Endif
    #Commit
    FILTRANS=0
  Next
  Filter [F:SOH]

  GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR

  #NUMPED = ""
  #REQUEST="SELECT SOHNUM_0 FROM SORDER WHERE CUSORDREF_0='"+[F:ZINPE]ZREF1+"'"
  #For (Char NUMPEDIDO(50)) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [XXX]
  #  NUMPED = [F:XXX]NUMPEDIDO
  #Next


  Return

$AB_SAL_PEDIDO
  #Rollback
  FILTRANS=0
  Call ROLL From GLOCK
  If GROLL : Return : Endif

$ROLL_SAL_PEDIDO
  #Rollback
  FLTRANS = 0
  Call ROLL From GLOCK
  If GROLL : Return : Endif


$SALDAR_PEDIDO_NEW

  Local Char VALBOUT(250),PARBOUT(250)(1..20)
  Local Char NUMPED(50)
  Local Char REFERENCIA(100)
  Local Char CRITERIO(255)(5)
  Local Integer WZGSERVEUR
  Local Char CURRDATE(50)
  Local Char CURRTIME(50)
  Local Char CURRDATETIME_STR(100)
  Local Char REQUEST(100)
  Local Char PEDABIERTO(40)
  Local Decimal CTDRUPTURA

  WZGSERVEUR = GSERVEUR
  GSERVEUR = 1

  CURRDATE = (num$(day(date$))) + "/" + num$(month(date$)) + "/" + num$(year(date$))
  CURRTIME = num$(time$)
  CURRDATETIME_STR =CURRDATE + " " + CURRTIME



CRITERIO(1)="([F:SOH]BPCORD='43001746' OR [F:SOH]BPCORD='43002136') AND [F:SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT='' AND [F:SOH]ZFIMPEDMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENCONMKT<>'' AND "
CRITERIO(2)="[F:SOH]ZFIMSHIPMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENTRACMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENSHIPMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ORDSTA=1"

  Filter [F:SOH] Where evalue(CRITERIO)
  For [F:SOH]

    NUMPED=[F:SOH]SOHNUM
    REFERENCIA=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF

    PEDABIERTO=""
    REQUEST="SELECT LCKSYM_0 FROM APLLCK WHERE LCKSYM_0='SOH"+NUMPED+"'"
    For (Char NUMPED(100)) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [YYY]
      PEDABIERTO = [F:YYY]NUMPED
    Next

    If PEDABIERTO="" Then
      #Comprobamos que el pedido tenga algún artículo en ruptura
      CTDRUPTURA=0
      REQUEST="SELECT SUM(SHTQTY_0) AS CANTIDAD FROM SORDERQ WHERE SOHNUM_0='"+NUMPED+"'"
      For (Decimal CTDRUP) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [ZZZ]
        CTDRUPTURA = [F:ZZZ]CTDRUP
      Next

      If CTDRUPTURA>0 Then
        Call ECR_TRACE("SALDANDO PEDIDO: "+NUMPED,0) From GESECRAN


        #Update [ZINTE] Where ZREF1=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF With ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR

        GACTION = "TRTCLESOH"
        PARBOUT(1)=NUMPED
        PARBOUT(2)=""
        FLGEXE=1

        Call TRAITE_CHAR(VALBOUT,PARBOUT,"","TRTVENCDE","",1,"XYTRTVENCDE") From GTRAITE

        [SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR
        Rewrite [SOH]

        #Update [SOH2] Where [SOH2]SOHNUM=[F:SOH]SOHNUM With [SOH2]ZFCONFSALMKT='DD'
        #If fstat
        #  GOK=0 : Call FSTA("ZSALDO") From GLOCK : STA=14
        #Endif
        #If GOK<0 : Goto ROLL_IMP_SALDO
        #Elsif !GOK : Goto AB_IMP_SALDO
        #Endif



        #GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR
      Endif
    Else
      Call ECR_TRACE("******** PEDIDO "+NUMPED+ " NO SE PUDO SALDAR. ABIERTO EN OTRO PUESTO",0) From GESECRAN
    Endif
  Next
  Filter [F:SOH]

  GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR

  FILTRANS=0
Return

$AB_IMP_SALDO
  #Rollback
  FILTRANS=0
  Call ROLL From GLOCK
  If GROLL : Return : Else : Goto SALDAR_PEDIDO_NEW : Endif

$ROLL_IMP_SALDO
  #Rollback
  FLTRANS = 0
  Call ROLL From GLOCK
  If GROLL : Return : Else : Goto SALDAR_PEDIDO_NEW : Endif

$SALDAR_PEDIDO_2
  Local Char VALBOUT(250),PARBOUT(250)(1..20)

        GACTION = "TRTCLESOH"
        PARBOUT(1)="PEC-17-300-00005"
        PARBOUT(2)=""
        FLGEXE=1


        Call TRAITE_CHAR(VALBOUT,PARBOUT,"","TRTVENCDE","",1,"XYTRTVENCDE") From GTRAITE




Return

$SALDAR_PEDIDO_TODORUPTURA

  Local Char VALBOUT(250),PARBOUT(250)(1..20)
  Local Char NUMPED(50)
  Local Char REFERENCIA(100)
  Local Char CRITERIO(255)(5)
  Local Integer WZGSERVEUR
  Local Char CURRDATE(50)
  Local Char CURRTIME(50)
  Local Char CURRDATETIME_STR(100)
  Local Char REQUEST(100)
  Local Char PEDABIERTO(40)
  Local Decimal CTDRUPTURA
  Local Decimal QTYPED

  WZGSERVEUR = GSERVEUR
  GSERVEUR = 1

  CURRDATE = (num$(day(date$))) + "/" + num$(month(date$)) + "/" + num$(year(date$))
  CURRTIME = num$(time$)
  CURRDATETIME_STR =CURRDATE + " " + CURRTIME



CRITERIO(1)="([F:SOH]BPCORD='43001746' OR [F:SOH]BPCORD='43002136') AND [F:SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT='' AND [F:SOH]ZFIMPEDMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENCONMKT<>'' AND "
CRITERIO(2)="[F:SOH]ZFIMSHIPMKT<>'' AND [F:SOH]ZFENTRACMKT='' AND [F:SOH]ZFENSHIPMKT='' AND [F:SOH]ORDSTA=1 AND [F:SOH]ZFENDEVMKT<>''"

  Filter [F:SOH] Where evalue(CRITERIO)
  For [F:SOH]

    NUMPED=[F:SOH]SOHNUM
    REFERENCIA=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF

    PEDABIERTO=""
    REQUEST="SELECT LCKSYM_0 FROM APLLCK WHERE LCKSYM_0='SOH"+NUMPED+"'"
    For (Char NUMPED(100)) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [YYY]
      PEDABIERTO = [F:YYY]NUMPED
    Next

    If PEDABIERTO="" Then
      #Comprobamos que el pedido tenga algún artículo en ruptura
      CTDRUPTURA=0
      REQUEST="SELECT SUM(SHTQTY_0) AS CANTIDAD FROM SORDERQ WHERE SOHNUM_0='"+NUMPED+"'"
      For (Decimal CTDRUP) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [ZZZ]
        CTDRUPTURA = [F:ZZZ]CTDRUP
      Next

      QTYPED=0
      REQUEST="SELECT SUM(QTY_0) AS CANTIDAD FROM SORDERQ WHERE SOHNUM_0='"+NUMPED+"'"
      For (Decimal CTDPED) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [ZZZ]
        QTYPED = [F:ZZZ]CTDPED
      Next

      If CTDRUPTURA=QTYPED Then
        Call ECR_TRACE("SALDANDO PEDIDO: "+NUMPED,0) From GESECRAN


        #Update [ZINTE] Where ZREF1=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF With ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR

        GACTION = "TRTCLESOH"
        PARBOUT(1)=NUMPED
        PARBOUT(2)=""
        FLGEXE=1

        Call TRAITE_CHAR(VALBOUT,PARBOUT,"","TRTVENCDE","",1,"XYTRTVENCDE") From GTRAITE

        [SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR
        Rewrite [SOH]

        #Update [SOH2] Where [SOH2]SOHNUM=[F:SOH]SOHNUM With [SOH2]ZFCONFSALMKT='DD'
        #If fstat
        #  GOK=0 : Call FSTA("ZSALDO") From GLOCK : STA=14
        #Endif
        #If GOK<0 : Goto ROLL_IMP_SALDO
        #Elsif !GOK : Goto AB_IMP_SALDO
        #Endif



        #GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR
      Endif
    Else
      Call ECR_TRACE("******** PEDIDO "+NUMPED+ " NO SE PUDO SALDAR. ABIERTO EN OTRO PUESTO",0) From GESECRAN
    Endif
  Next
  Filter [F:SOH]

  GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR

  FILTRANS=0
Return


$SALDAR_PEDIDO_EXCEL

  Local Char VALBOUT(250),PARBOUT(250)(1..20)
  Local Char NUMPED(50)
  Local Char REFERENCIA(100)
  Local Char CRITERIO(255)
  Local Integer WZGSERVEUR
  Local Char CURRDATE(50)
  Local Char CURRTIME(50)
  Local Char CURRDATETIME_STR(100)
  Local Char REQUEST(100)
  Local Char PEDABIERTO(40)
  Local Decimal CTDRUPTURA

  WZGSERVEUR = GSERVEUR
  GSERVEUR = 1

  CURRDATE = (num$(day(date$))) + "/" + num$(month(date$)) + "/" + num$(year(date$))
  CURRTIME = num$(time$)
  CURRDATETIME_STR =CURRDATE + " " + CURRTIME



Filter [F:ZPP]
For [F:ZPP]
CRITERIO=
& "[F:SOH]BPCORD='43001746' AND [F:SOH]SOHNUM='"+[F:ZPP]SOHNUM+"'"

  Filter [F:SOH] Where evalue(CRITERIO)
  For [F:SOH]

    NUMPED=[F:SOH]SOHNUM
    REFERENCIA=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF

    PEDABIERTO=""
    REQUEST="SELECT LCKSYM_0 FROM APLLCK WHERE LCKSYM_0='SOH"+NUMPED+"'"
    For (Char NUMPED(100)) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [YYY]
      PEDABIERTO = [F:YYY]NUMPED
    Next

    If PEDABIERTO="" Then
      #Comprobamos que el pedido tenga algún artículo en ruptura
      CTDRUPTURA=0
      REQUEST="SELECT SUM(SHTQTY_0) AS CANTIDAD FROM SORDERQ WHERE SOHNUM_0='"+NUMPED+"'"
      For (Decimal CTDRUP) From "5" Sql REQUEST As [ZZZ]
        CTDRUPTURA = [F:ZZZ]CTDRUP
      Next

      #If CTDRUPTURA>0 Then
        Call ECR_TRACE("SALDANDO PEDIDO: "+NUMPED,0) From GESECRAN


        #Update [ZINTE] Where ZREF1=[F:SOH]CUSORDREF With ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR

        GACTION = "TRTCLESOH"
        PARBOUT(1)=NUMPED
        PARBOUT(2)=""
        FLGEXE=1

        Call TRAITE_CHAR(VALBOUT,PARBOUT,"","TRTVENCDE","",1,"XYTRTVENCDE") From GTRAITE

        [SOH]ZFCONFSALMKT=CURRDATETIME_STR
        Rewrite [SOH]

        #Update [SOH2] Where [SOH2]SOHNUM=[F:SOH]SOHNUM With [SOH2]ZFCONFSALMKT='DD'
        #If fstat
        #  GOK=0 : Call FSTA("ZSALDO") From GLOCK : STA=14
        #Endif
        #If GOK<0 : Goto ROLL_IMP_SALDO
        #Elsif !GOK : Goto AB_IMP_SALDO
        #Endif



        #GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR
      #Endif
    Else
      Call ECR_TRACE("******** PEDIDO "+NUMPED+ " NO SE PUDO SALDAR. ABIERTO EN OTRO PUESTO",0) From GESECRAN
    Endif
  Next
  Filter [F:SOH]
Next
Filter [F:ZPP]
  GSERVEUR = WZGSERVEUR

  FILTRANS=0
Return

